ĮKENNETH NELSON
1930         (ACTOR)          1993    
(TEXAS)                          (LONDON)
       Life was FANTASTIC      
                                      NAOMI"∂
≥Nowhere is more loved than this treasured
place where joyous times are shared with
family, friends and all who stop to wonder al
the beauty surrounding them. Christine Kitchen."∑
īPeace be with you. Love to all.
Hope for our children.
Cherished son, brother, uncle, friend.
Adventurer and actor.
At one with nature, his spirit flies free.
Wise John Glynn."Ĺ
ļIn memory of
Derek Lane
From a select number of friends who spent many happy
hours in his company and together enjoyed the splendour
of this city and the tranquility of these gardens"ĺ
